name: alloc::collections::btree::fix::<impl collections::btree::node::Handle<collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Mut<'a>, K, V, collections::btree::node::marker::Internal>, collections::btree::node::marker::KV>>::fix_right_child
doc:
Stocks up the right child, assuming the left child isn't underfull, and
 provisions an extra element to allow merging its children in turn
 without becoming underfull.
 Returns wherever the right child ended up.
